        &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=ReplyQuote&amp;REPLY_ID=38962&amp;TOPIC_ID=4886&amp;FORUM_ID=3&amp;CAT_ID=1&amp;Forum_Title=Necromancer+Game+Guides&amp;Topic_Title=Four+blues+needed+to+hit+55&amp;M="><img src="icon_reply_topic.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Reply with Quote" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         NEVER fear on this island you will get adds 9 out of 10 times.  The pet can easily tank them with a BoD and a dooming (snare them so when they turn to run they dont go up the island they just stand there and die) from you and lose about 25% hp.  If you bod the cyclops and shadowbound the pet you can take them down no problem.  This is very good now that pet takes no xp so you dont have to waist mana ks'in pet.  You can make a good deal of money here to.  I went through 51 here and some of 52.  </P><P>Azrayel<BR>55 Defiler<BR>Prexus</P><P>Edited by - Azrayel on 06/11/2002  21:45:55</P><P>Edited by - Azrayel on 06/11/2002  21:46:41<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
